{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"5ff00d92-2614-4ecd-975a-4d17b27a2833","content":"No repo files to inspect — this is a general guidance question. Here's how to migrate:\n\n### 1. Replace `VSTest@3` with `DotNetCoreCLI@2` (or a plain `dotnet test` script)\n\n```yaml\n# Before (VSTest runner)\n- task: VSTest@3\n  inputs:\n    testAssemblies: '**/*Tests.dll'\n    runSettingsFile: test.runsettings\n    codeCoverageEnabled: true\n\n# After (Microsoft.Testing.Platform via dotnet test)\n- task: DotNetCoreCLI@2\n  displayName: 'Run tests'\n  inputs:\n    command: test\n    projects: '**/*Tests.csproj'\n    arguments: >-\n      --configuration $(BuildConfiguration)\n      --logger \"trx;LogFileName=TestResults.trx\"\n      --results-directory $(Agent.TempDirectory)/TestResults\n      --collect \"Code Coverage\"\n```\n\n### 2. Enable Microsoft.Testing.Platform in each test project\n\nAdd to every test `.csproj` (or a `Directory.Build.props`):\n\n```xml\n<PropertyGroup>\n  <EnableMSTestRunner>true</EnableMSTestRunner>   <!-- for MSTest -->\n  <TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport>true</TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport>\n</PropertyGroup>\n```\n\n### 3. Publish results & coverage\n\n```yaml\n- task: PublishTestResults@2\n  displayName: 'Publish TRX results'\n  condition: always()\n  inputs:\n    testResultsFormat: VSTest\n    testResultsFiles: '$(Agent.TempDirectory)/TestResults/**/*.trx'\n\n- task: PublishCodeCoverageResults@2\n  displayName: 'Publish code coverage'\n  condition: always()\n  inputs:\n    summaryFileLocation: '$(Agent.TempDirectory)/TestResults/**/*.coverage'\n```\n\n### Key points\n\n- **`--logger trx`** produces the same `.trx` files you had before.\n- **`--collect \"Code Coverage\"`** replaces `codeCoverageEnabled: true`.\n- Set **`condition: always()`** on publish tasks so results are uploaded even when tests fail.\n- If you used a `.runsettings` file, pass it with `--settings test.runsettings`.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"1be7acec-8742-44b0-a404-005d80ddb482","outputTokens":569,"requestId":"4815:23D333:3113DB2:35A865B:69FBE2AE"},"id":"30bded7f-2da7-4353-a33c-a952c3e45dce","timestamp":"2026-05-07T00:54:16.525Z","parentId":"adee7607-a331-4da7-9b71-591243e46236"}
